title: S16 Ep70: Trail of Bigfoot: Tracking the Enigmatic Giants of the Forest w/Mike Dupler
itunes:title: Trail of Bigfoot: Tracking the Enigmatic Giants of the Forest w/Mike Dupler
description:
Darkness Radio presents Trail of Bigfoot: Tracking the Enigmatic Giants of the Forest with Mike Dupler

Dave & Tim head deep into the out of doors to explore claims of Bigfoot with guests Mike Dupler.
Mike Dupler has been seeking and having experiences with the shy woodland creature, uncovering unique communication techniques, strange habits and more.

Get his book here: https://amzn.to/3qm5Y06

Follow Mike here: www.FaceBook.com/AuthorMikeDupler
